        "lens": "correctness",
        "summary": "The submitCommand in prepareDispatchArtifacts hardcodes the execution path to `node packages/audit-code/audit-code.mjs`, which will fail when auditing any repository other than the auditor-lambda repository itself.",
        "affected_files": [
          {
            "path": "packages/audit-code/src/cli/dispatch.ts",
